Get insight into how well the Contact Support Form and Case Deflection components actually deflect cases from being created.
Using the Case Deflection Dashboard, get real-time metrics on potential and confirmed case deflections, the most helpful articles and discussions, and the least helpful articles and discussions.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions
Manage Custom Report Types

To create custom report types so users can analyze which articles and discussions are most useful in deflecting cases in a community.
Create a public folder for the reports. This requires Manage Public Reports permission.

After completing these steps, a folder of community case deflection metrics reports is available to your users on the Reports home page.
title: Analyzing Community Case Deflection Metrics in Salesforce
